---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout title="Monthly Q&A — Thee Rainers">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="description" content="Monthly live Q&A included with every paid product. One hour. Real-time diagnosis through the 7 levers." />
  </Fragment>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 pt-32 md:pt-40 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] gap-16 md:gap-24 items-start">

        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-8">Monthly · Included with every paid product</p>
          <h1 class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[0.82] mb-10">Live Q&A.<br/>Real diagnosis.</h1>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/50 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-[480px]">
            The protocol gives you the system. The library gives you the depth. This is where you bring what is not transferring — and we map it to the lever in real time.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/35 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-[480px]">
            One hour. One Saturday per month. No fluff, no performance, no upsell. You show up with a problem. We apply the operating system to it — live. Included with any paid product or Workshop.
          </p>

          <!-- Next session callout -->
          <div class="border-l-2 border-[#D4A373] pl-6 mb-10">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">Next Session</p>
            <!-- TODO: POST-JUNE-27 DATE SWAP -->
            <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A] uppercase tracking-tighter text-2xl leading-tight">Saturday, June 13</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm mt-1">1 hour · Live · Camera on · Real-time diagnosis</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Registration Form -->
          <div class="border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 bg-[#F6F6F6] p-8 max-w-[480px]">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Reserve your place</p>
            <form id="qa-form" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
              <input
                type="email"
                id="qa-email"
                required
                placeholder="your@email.com"
                class="border border-[#0A0A0A]/15 bg-transparent px-5 py-4 text-[#0A0A0A] text-sm focus:border-[#D4A373] focus:outline-none transition-colors duration-200 placeholder:text-[#0A0A0A]/20"
              />
              <button
                type="submit"
                id="qa-submit"
                class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-8 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white"
              >
                Register →
              </button>
            </form>
            <p id="qa-success" class="hidden text-[#D4A373] text-sm tracking-wide mt-4">Registered. Details sent before June 13.</p> <!-- TODO: POST-JUNE-27 DATE SWAP -->
            <p id="qa-error" class="hidden text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm mt-4">Something went wrong. Try again.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-[2px]">
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-8">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Perceptual</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">You are not reading the cue early enough. Bring the sparring problem. We diagnose the perceptual leak and prescribe the drill.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-8">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Mechanical</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">The chain is breaking between the floor and the fist. Show the movement. We find the break. One correction — not five.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#F6F6F6] border border-[#0A0A0A]/8 p-8">
            <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Existential</p>
            <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">The mechanics are there in drilling. They dissolve under pressure. Layer 3 problem — identity, presence, internal standard. We address it directly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scripture + Upgrade -->
  <section class="bg-white px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-24 border-t border-[#0A0A0A]/8">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-end justify-between gap-16">
      <div class="max-w-[560px]">
        <p class="font-black text-[#0A0A0A]/55 uppercase tracking-tighter text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-[0.88] mb-6">"Iron sharpens iron, and one man sharpens another."</p>
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-10">Proverbs 27:17</p>
        <p class="text-[#0A0A0A]/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">The free tier builds the foundation. The Q&A is where the system compounds — in community, under a standard, with direct access to the architect. Unlock it with any paid product.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 shrink-0">
        <a href="/vault" class="blue-btn inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#0057FF] text-[#0057FF] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#0057FF] hover:text-white">
          Enter the Vault →
        </a>
        <a href="/command" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border border-[#0A0A0A]/15 text-[#0A0A0A]/30 bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:border-[#0A0A0A]/30 hover:text-[#0A0A0A]/50">
          Apply for 1-on-1 →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('qa-form') as HTMLFormElement | null;
  const submit = document.getElementById('qa-submit') as HTMLButtonElement | null;
  const success = document.getElementById('qa-success')!;
  const error = document.getElementById('qa-error')!;

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    if (submit) { submit.disabled = true; submit.textContent = 'Registering...'; }
    error.classList.add('hidden');

    const email = (document.getElementById('qa-email') as HTMLInputElement).value.trim();

    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/lead-capture', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ email, source: 'qa-registration', full_name: '' }),
      });
      const body = await res.json() as { success: boolean };
      if (body.success) {
        form?.classList.add('hidden');
        success.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else { throw new Error(); }
    } catch {
      error.classList.remove('hidden');
      if (submit) { submit.disabled = false; submit.textContent = 'Register →'; }
    }
  });
</script>
